{
  "stem": "10478.2",
  "chunk_idx": 11,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 14.8,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 97,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And I decided to quit, and to keep on working for helping people who were in hiding.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 98,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I gave up paying job.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 98,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "That's right.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 98,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Yes.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 99,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yeah.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 100,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Groceries.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 100,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "We used girls for delivering food stamps, because girls are not arrested.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 100,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "If you are a man at 18, 19, 20, they would pick you up and send you to full work in Germany.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 100,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "So they were-- they can easy do something than the men are doing.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 101,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "No.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 101,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "That's right.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 101,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Yes.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 101,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Of course, for them there was no danger to be picked up.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 102,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Oh, yes.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 102,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Oh, yeah.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 102,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "No problem.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 103,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "They were quite willing, yes.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 104,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "That's right.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 104,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Yes.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 104,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "For example, I got-- I had conflict in Amsterdam.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 104,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And the family, they asked me-- two friend, two student-- if they could visit them.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 104,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And they had a little baby who was 12 days old.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 104,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And they asked me for a hiding place for the baby.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 105,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So I went back to Maastricht by train.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 105,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And I couldn't find a-- a place right away.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 105,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "So we asked my parents if it was OK that the baby could stay at our place for a couple days until we find a place.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 105,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And my mom agreed to that.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 106,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And then took a girl along with me, went back to Amsterdam, pick up the baby in a little basket.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 106,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And acting as a married couple we went back to Maastricht.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 106,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And the baby came to my parents' place.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 106,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And after a few days, my mom said-- my mom said, we like the baby so much.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 106,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "We can stay here.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 106,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "Stay there till the end of the war.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 107,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "That's right.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 107,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Yes.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 108,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yeah.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 108,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Yeah.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 109,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Can stay as well.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 110,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "A Jewish baby.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 110,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Yes.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 111,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "My sister did.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 111,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And Fritz did part of duties.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 111,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "He gave the bottle, and whatever that he could do, yeah.",
      "word_count": 11
    }
  ],
